+## 接口
+
+- 无前置依赖
+
+## 步骤
+
+- [ ] **Step 1: 更新 README.md**
+
+在 backend/README.md 中添加：
+
+```markdown
+## Getting Started
+
+### Prerequisites
+
+- Node.js >= 18
+- PostgreSQL
+- Redis
+
+### Installation
+
+```bash
+npm install
+```
+
+### Configuration
+
+Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and configure your environment variables.
+
+### Database Setup
+
+```bash
+npx prisma migrate dev
+npx prisma generate
+```
+
+### Running the App
+
+```bash
+# development
+npm run dev
+
+# production
+npm run build
+npm run start:prod
+```
+
+### Testing
+
+```bash
+# unit tests
+npm run test
+
+# e2e tests
+npm run test:e2e
+```
+
+## API Endpoints
+
+### Authentication
+
+- `POST /api/auth/register` - Register a new user
